1
00:00:01,859 --> 00:00:02,960
Hello, friend.

2
00:00:05,240 --> 00:00:06,320
Hello, Mom. Hello, brother.

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,720
Şükran, come over here for a moment.

4
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:09,919
All right, sir.

5
00:00:11,339 --> 00:00:11,820
What's up?

6
00:00:12,279 --> 00:00:14,339
If not, then no—not even a jug of water for us.

7
00:00:14,779 --> 00:00:16,199
The faucet is over there, the bucket is over there.

8
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:17,879
The water is yours now—congratulations.

9
00:00:18,379 --> 00:00:20,260
We’ve got nothing to do with water, bro.

10
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:21,199
That's why.

11
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:22,140
Are you available?

12
00:00:23,019 --> 00:00:24,000
What am I suited for?

13
00:00:24,239 --> 00:00:24,980
Blue jay.

14
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:27,480
What am I doing?

15
00:00:27,660 --> 00:00:29,039
You saw us in the garden.

16
00:00:29,039 --> 00:00:30,460
Did you think I was a gardener?

17
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:32,979
I’m Arif, Mr. Özgür’s driver.

18
00:00:33,380 --> 00:00:33,700
Arif.

19
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:36,799
I am also the World Cycling Box Champion, Atilla Baytar.

20
00:00:37,159 --> 00:00:38,179
Hehe he.

21
00:00:39,179 --> 00:00:40,039
Are you giving us a hard time?

